<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قاله المزي في "التحفة<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(٤/ ١٦٠)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
